Section: misc
Priority: optional
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)

Package: znapzend
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, perl 
Description: High performance open source ZFS backup with mbuffer and ssh support
 Znapzend is leveraging ZFS and ssh creating flexible backup solution with
 features including mbuffer support, fileset-based configuration,
 flexible backup locations, progressive thining, online backup scheduler
 and flexible snapshot naming.
